name: Remnants by Nullish
description: Each piece of the collection captures the aftermath of a supernova explosion located in its own corner of the universe. Some are only hundreds of light years away from us, and others, billions. Nullish Labs' Imaging System translates telescope data outside the visible light spectrum into mesmerizing patterns of cosmic debris left behind by the destruction of a star. Remnants symbolize the cycle of life, death, and rebirth.
